title: d
author: Yxkly
pages:
#- Mithras, god of oaths and honesty, champion of the light, slayer of daemons, judge of the dead, patron god of legionaries and monarchs , lord of Sol Invictus, master of the zodiacs, slayer of Tauros, the one birthed from the cosmos and
#- reborn in the earth, has spoken to me. He has instructed me to teach all of his glory, guide them to the light, and purge the evil from the world. Mithras will bring all to paradise, but only if he is praised by the enitrity of this world, and for
#- that to happen he has made me his voice. I, cmf23099, am the Voice of Mithras untill paradise is reached and the darkness purged. I will speak his orders and lessons, I will express his anger and joy, and I will lead the world to glory in his stead.
#- But for me to do that, I will need people to listen, befome my followers and in turn, follwers of Mithras. Et benedictus Deus Mithrae!
#- 